{"tid":152624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好垃圾,曹星如呢D排骨精都要吹奏...","createTime":"2017-03-12T02:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T08:15:42.000Z","uid":82845,"like":40,"dislike":233,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbf783119e1205e0c5f71a6666afb3f893dc11a","tid":152624,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好垃圾,連排骨精都要吹奏<br />\n係自卑到強行要搵野吹奏自己<br />\n所以拎曹星如出黎<br />\n吹到佢世界第一<br />\n第一就係第一<br />\n不如係營養不良中既第一<br />\n香港人就最鐘意係次一級既比賽中稱霸<br />\n然後自吹自雷<br />\n<br />\n超蒼蠅級個級數就好似殘奧咁<br />\n蘇華偉又係拎出黎出捧<br />\n我唔係話蘇生唔努力<br />\n但係殘奧個選手池有幾大?<br />\n只要努力+上傷殘輕d就好易拎獎<br />\n蘇生係應該表揚<br />\n但係香港人剩係拎得出蘇生<br />\n好應該檢討下<br />\n唔係仲係到自慰 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/1004651_10201754750015661_1361071148_n-528x446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2F1004651_10201754750015661_1361071148_n-528x446.jpg&h=2f498820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曹普星如連胸肌都無<br />\n難聽D講<br />\n係街到比南亞狗打<br />\n曹生都未必敢自衛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum2.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6689118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum2.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DBW%26message%3D6689118&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0b6a4d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum2.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6689118</a>"},{"pid":"130f9d325174b35acef4f40cd6c1e5c78630cc43","tid":152624,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"有人開始做野，怕香港之光太光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a98681c5fada986cc5719f401f2154d788a792b","tid":152624,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e576878ed41e880db2b2dc7be19294f9cd01811","tid":152624,"uid":19191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"香港人係鐘意垃圾架 不如你番大陸啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be1a68d55a62c4c2b9fc078d402c29b52971b10","tid":152624,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:17:29.000Z","msg":"支那五毛狗真係好垃圾<br />\n唔抵得香港人有個世界冠軍"},{"pid":"4b23110cabb242f1921c2ee721faacf6c6fa9fab","tid":152624,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"我一早都話<br />\n唱衰香港人係支那同化香港計劃一部分<br />\n支那自己支那狗質素差<br />\n要管比佢地文化水平高既香港一定會出問題<br />\n而香港人都唔服<br />\n所以近來先有咁多人借小小事就話香港人點點點<br />\n最多支那五毛狗用既格式就係<br />\n1:香港人唔配有乜乜乜<br />\n2:香港同支那冇咩分別<br />\n先打擊香港人<br />\n等香港人自以爲水平差<br />\n咁對於比生番國支那管治時心理抵抗會減抵<br />\n大家睇路"},{"pid":"bf5b429cc79ae09da47a1aa849802e527992561f","tid":152624,"uid":57867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母已負評"},{"pid":"860b855706c928c31ddd0c0586c06896c5a460f4","tid":152624,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"咁樓主上去打啦，講咁多做乜柒姐"},{"pid":"3e82ba874756a06abc0465a39589454c019cbf42","tid":152624,"uid":52511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"樓主見到曹星如咪又係淆撚哂底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4ef9cfa0de517230d0a792547e486b91adf2b3","tid":152624,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"樓主俾人同曹星如比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大怨氣"},{"pid":"bf0d2f4a066ecde28f7fa57926d7479418b5afce","tid":152624,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"奏你老母"},{"pid":"96e60a826d0d57789c5efe76d38c7ce99c45bc23","tid":152624,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"睇住d柒頭支持佢，以為香港人好打得就好笑<br />\n同不停用李小龍嚟自我感覺良好嘅東亞病夫冇分別<br />\n<br />\n蠅咩嘢量級，實戰